[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    102[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## Pseudocode-to-Python Consistency
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    103[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    104[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | Main Recipe Pseudocode Step | Python Implementation | Consistent? |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    105[0m:[38;5;10m[49m |---|---|---|
