[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    107[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | `estimate_demand(case_history, known_changes)` | `estimate_demand(services)` | Yes (simplified: pre-calculated demand in input file vs. computed from history) |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    108[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | `formulate_model(...)` | `formulate_model(...)` | Yes (see notes below) |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    109[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | `solve_and_extract(model, solver_config)` | `solve_model(model, x, blocks, services)` | Mostly (missing IIS computation for infeasible case) |
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    110[0m:[38;5;10m[49m | `analyze_solution(...)` | `analyze_solution(...)` | Yes |
